language Essence 1.3

given v: int(1..)
given b: int(1..)
given r: int(1..)
given k: int(1..)
given lambda: int(1..)
find incidence: matrix indexed by [int(1..v), int(1..b)] of int(0..1)
such that
    and([sum([incidence[point, block] | block : int(1..b)]) = r | point : int(1..v)]),
    and([sum([incidence[point, block] | point : int(1..v)]) = k | block : int(1..b)]),
    and([and([sum([incidence[p1, block] * incidence[p2, block] | block : int(1..b)]) = lambda | p2 : int(p1 + 1..v)])
             | p1 : int(1..v)])

